tip.text: I love the chiffon cakes!! So good. Also the strawberry roll is amazing too.
The stir fried duck dish is yummy! The white coffee was great too! Recommended.
The meatball is overrated. Spicy vodka rigatoni is amazing! Also love the desserts, esp the banana flambé.
